Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani mo nai tadatada tsudzuku sora
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.43,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing is endless as the everlasting sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,5,,Nani hitotsu te ni todokanai yōna
Dialogue: 1,0:00:16.43,0:00:19.46,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Nothing out there that is out of my reach
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hi no biru no sukima kara mieta gaitō ni
Dialogue: 1,0:00:19.46,0:00:25.77,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Tonight's streetlights in between buildings sites\NAre too bright on me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,5,,Watashi ga nanimonona no ka tte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.77,0:00:29.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For so long I \NDidn't know who I am
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,5,,Utau koto wa nanina no katte
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.98,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}What songs I sing \NAnd what songs I sang
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,5,,Ano hito ha ai o kuretakatte shiritaku mo nai
Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.98,0:00:37.85,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}For long enough that the one offering love \NDoesn't want to know me now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo itamunara kono itaminara
Dialogue: 1,0:00:37.85,0:00:43.86,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But even if you're getting hurt, \NEven if it hurts a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,5,,Mōsukoshi mōsukoshi itai gurai ga ī
Dialogue: 1,0:00:43.86,0:00:50.33,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}In a little more, just a little more\NThis pain will turn to joy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,5,,Kirainara kirai to ima kotoba ni shite
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.33,0:00:56.57,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Say you hate me, say all you want\NYour words don't frighten me a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,5,,Mienai ashita o koko de owara sete
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.57,0:01:02.37,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}Cause if you do, your tomorrow, \NUnseen before, will die for good
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,5,,Demo an'nani aishita kon'nani aishiteru
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.37,0:01:08.88,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}But how I loved you before,\NI love you now just as much
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,600)}Sono shiawase no hitotsude ī oboete ite
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.88,0:01:18.82,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,600)}And how sincerely happy we were in old days\NI will never forget
Comment: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.79,Song,,0,0,0,,{OP ED border}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Free lap! Splendid! I want you to know, sweetie,\Nright now you're shining brighter than ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded. \NWinner - Oumi Shunichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! \NOumi won again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded. \NWinner - Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Final score - 2064 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhere in the depths of your heart, \Nyou sincerely hate pachislot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.19,0:02:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You say I actually hate pachislot? \NWhy would you suggest such nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.07,0:02:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to hate it. \NAnd to prove it to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To fight you as soon as I can, \NI must keep winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:39.35,Song,sign,0,0,0,,{\fade(900,700)\an8\c&HFFFFFF&\bord1\shad2\blur1\3c&H6D5B95&\4c&H55397C&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\4a&H41&\fscx117\fscy88}Episode 6 \N {\fs86}Spark
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One of our instructors went on a sudden hiatus, \Nand tomorrow is my day off...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, even though tomorrow is Saturday, \Nwouldn't you be so kind as to replace them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'd ask someone else, \Nbut no one else is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have not yet attended courses \Non healthy breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Running properly is not such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.17,0:02:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Would a cafe owner allow a day off for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? I'll have to manage this place on my own \Nthis time? Don't worry, it's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is doing fairly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A worthy adversary for us, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, you plan to watch it until the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all, I was just waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to celebrate our recent conquests. \NWell, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it. \NBut I came here on bike...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:43.52,Song,,0,0,0,,Game is concluded. Winner - Yoshino Sayaka. Final score: 2061 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about dropping at my place? \NYou can stay for night. Won't have to worry about driving drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it. \NWe're both one victory away from the Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If it goes well for you, \NI won't have to regret losing that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had been more careful then, \NI could even get promoted before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing personal, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. \NI'll catch up soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen. Sorry, but I'm not stopping any time soon. I will go on winning until I'm at the very top.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That is easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The hottest clashes seem to happen \Non the borders between classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Borders between classes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Like between Members and Knights. \NThe difference in power is apparent then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the first real difficulty is the knights level, \Nand not everyone can withstand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not everyone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, which only makes Daiba Ryo more ominous, \Nsince this guy went through 3 of such promotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, on the other hand, \Nit makes the road more interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.91,0:04:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,To the one reclining in his throne - \Nthe Ultimate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I was even thinking \Nabout taking his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as your humble servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I can already see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, how dare I, your majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's drink to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I have to manage all by myself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where's my rice omelet?{i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How unusual...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so. Right now, Master is having \Nunbelievably hard times all by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.34,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, really? Ginya, please! \NSince I couldn't come today, please help out Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Oumi Shunichi handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this womanizer also there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.33,0:05:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanged up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We are glad to see you in our cafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Please, have a sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I see my sake today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.96,0:05:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. It's on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for a coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.85,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But our coffee is the best one around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You must try it, as Shibaura's special brand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who else ordered a rice omelet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Two more spaghetti sets. \NBut no coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, on the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks for choosing our place!\NWe'll wait for you again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I could use one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Until you two showed up, \Nit was beyond saving today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Yuri who asked us to help.\NTo please Yuri, I'm willing to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.84,0:06:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Except she asked me only!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, don't you have to be in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah. I already called it and asked for a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why this whole day \NI'll dedicate to helping Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I don't pay barely as much as the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need any money from you.\NYuri's love for me will cover all the bills.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid, I don't even have that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone goes nuts their own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.47,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it? Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, editor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What, just a boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up talking to him! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, not a single one is good?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That is usually the case,\Nbut not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Should I rewrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Teresa sure has peculiar hobbies, \Nand pachislot is just a subject for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But only a pachislot fan would enjoy your writing. \NWe, in turn, want Teresa's fans to also buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Worst of all, time is running out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow noon is the manuscript deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow noon?{i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to think of something new until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood! You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be no more customers today,\Nyou can leave it to me and head home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Master. I was the one asked for help, \Nbut Oumi did most of the work ultimately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Working here was kinda fun. \NAnd I also got to wear another kind of apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But most importantly... Yuri will now know\Nhow responsible and practical I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she had no such opportunity before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Opportunity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Ever since you want to know,\Nthis fortuneless girl never had my phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute. I'll make the bitterest coffee \Nfor the doctor so that he finally wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't believe me? \NI'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they like so much about this ordinary game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd go straight home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I was too worried about the cafe.\NSo thank you both for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, alright! To help Yuri, \NI'm willing to go through fire and water!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! \NI wanted to give you my cell phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed by ourselves today, \Nso have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You two can also go now.\NFrom now on I can handle it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Why don't we go \Nto a French restaurant then, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? I want to treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We could...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}should{\i0}! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But we won't. Ever since I came here, \NI want you to teach me to play pachislot. Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, playing pachislot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of weird suggestion is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing,\Nbecause with Oumi Shunichi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,debit, credit, and bed it... \NRight! I'd love to bed this knowledge in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Ginya? Well? Will you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ginya is out of question. \NHe is too preoccupied with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,See? First, we add coins. \NThen gently shake this lever. And press the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, now it's Yuri's turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I put coins in this tray...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now try to catch the buttons' timings.\NThe bonus set is conspicuous one, so aim for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean those sevens?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!\NDamn, I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. For a first game, \Nthis is an amazing result.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Great. Then, let's try one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a born slotter!\NYuri, incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I really think you have a talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything special...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.73,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, actually, \NI think I'd rather finish at home. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.66,0:10:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best with the manuscript!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The music, in fact, consists of only seven tones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But by intertwining them in a complex pattern, \Nyou create a beautiful symphony.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In pachislot there are also 21 titles on each reel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And given that there are three of such reels, \Npotentially you can get more than 9000 combinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.80,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, pachislot is a decent cultural leisure \Nthat makes people's hearts happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what else can be said beside that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait though... Last time, Teresa seemingly \Nsaid something important to me. What was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.09,0:11:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Something about pachislot and piano rhythms..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your work. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pleasant surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, pachislot of all things... \NWhat made you suddenly change your mind about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just Ginya not being himself because of it. \NI couldn't help wondering what is so exciting about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning everyone! I have it, have it! \NYuri, for your deed, {\i1}thank you{\i0} to the deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a coffee, a hot one. \NNo need for bitterness. I have already woken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you also stay up late yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I got bored soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Got bored, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're so clever. \NMy little naive prodigy girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, cling on to my chest \Nin a gesture of gratitude!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Oumi. Five minutes into, \Nhe won't stop babbling, neglecting pachislot completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ode to Joy! Sing it with me, thou!" \NLike this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He was so distracting \NI couldn't track any numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi is at his best!\NNext time I will teach you myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when did you take that many pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be just a clerk now, \Nbut I actually wanted to become a reporter myself once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm experienced in both trades... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ginya. \NThis is something printworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well done in such a short time. \NYou did a great job of capturing Teresa's charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably underslept. \NGo home now and have a good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Willingly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an important game for promotion to Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let myself be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.02,0:13:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever happens today,\NI have no right to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's rules - starting at 200 points, \Nvictory at 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The participants may now \Nseat before the machines of their choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This one! For some reason it appeals to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.09,0:14:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What? If you're still alone, \Nyou can sit next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with her? \NSuch a pushy woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not into me,\Nsit somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But choose carefully who you start the game with. \NWe can flirt later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flirt {\i0}with me? \NIs Slothium a dating agency now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the mood, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, best of luck and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing next to the refined man \Nmight increase my chances of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Game starts in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nighttime writing has its downsides.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be yawning that wide, darling? \NAre you not nervous at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Sayaka.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's mutual. I am Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya... \NWhat a mature name you have!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you. \NWhy is this crazy woman following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind a female company, do you? \NThe fight is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Game starts in 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,4 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1... Start!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.43,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}Our Father, who art in machine, hallowed be thy play; \Nthy Small Factor come; thy will be done on reels as it is in heaven. \NGive us this day our daily Jackpot; \Nand lead us not into the miss, but deliver us from bad titles...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs20}Our Father, who art in machine, hallowed be thy play; \Nthy Small Factor come; thy will be done on reels as it is in heaven. \NGive us this day our daily Jackpot; \Nand lead us not into the miss, but deliver us from bad titles...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? \NWhy can't I score anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I made it this far, \NI have no choice but to drink and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Pressure. Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's predetermined, \Nregardless of our play?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I don't think that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I'm seeing someone \Nchatting so casually amidst the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is on her mind?\NDamn, missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew right away, \Nyou're dandy a man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When this game is over,\Nyou think we could go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.20,0:16:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayaka is not in the mood \Nto give this guy a single chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.78,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi is her favorite one for this game. \NI wonder how will Sayaka approach him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the pot-bellied one \Nseems to manage without her interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.78,0:16:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy survived last qualifiers by pure luck.\NDoes he have any chance of winning today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch... A misfortune. \NThat is one very ungodly machine. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... My Small Factor game strategy \Nis slowly but steadily starts paying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. What do you think of my proposal?\N{\i1}A date.{\i0} I'm free for the rest of the day you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on inside her head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed again... \NAlmost pulled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.65,0:17:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you! \NDon't talk to me until the game's conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.84,0:17:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My, why are you so harsh all of the sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it easy, remember to have fun. \NIt's just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I have so much trouble focusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. Hey, Otonashi Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, darling, do you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you come hear to talk heart to heart?\NQuit fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be sulky all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tired of sitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what? \NWill she ever settle down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to focus, the game is on!\NSuch a trifle won't distract me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how it is going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither the fervent prayer, nor the sincere devotion, nor the play in the Lord's name... Does not help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Hey hey, how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,For the love of God, don't come over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped if you don't want me to. \NI'm sure you'll have more luck next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the case... That is just her strategy. \NShe is disrupting other players' paces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you regained your confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like he cracked Sayaka's trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing is decided yet. \NOtonashi is still well behind her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he manage to disengage?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Otonashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Big!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,600)}Game is concluded. \NWinner - Otonashi Ginya. Final score...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you just press the buttons one by one. \NThe order is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:19:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna press them in reverse — do reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.18,0:20:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A reverse order works as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.43,0:20:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, you have such a pretty face!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.58,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I have a face of a person \Nsavvy in game's rules, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.35,0:20:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Bravo, Yuri! \NYour insight never ceases to amaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri, try the reverse order! \NIt's fun to look for new paths!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}New paths?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri has no way back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do to get a lot of coins at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first of all, \Ntry hitting Ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Riichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Riichi" is a mahjong term.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, should I add one more every game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to yell like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an impressive collection for one man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there are machines from all eras.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly do you need those photos for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pachislot history booklet. Once Ginya is back from his day off, I will task him with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll make sure Ginya doesn't slack off with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So many memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.63,0:20:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to play on this model a lot in my young days! \NYeah, truly, so much memories!
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.69,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}The heavy rain is over now, \NShadows have ceased to roam, \NEven summer itself has come to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.34,0:21:20.71,Song,,0,0,5,,Ame wa yande ita kage to aruide ita natsu ga owatte ita
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.69,0:21:34.27,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}My youth goes on, pushing me in my back with no rest,\NAnd the scarlet sky will soon start pouring water again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:34.29,Song,,0,0,5,,Seishun ga boku no senaka o oshite akai sora utsuru mizutamari
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.27,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}With my leg in a clutch, suddenly the sky shivered, \NSo unawares, making such stupid look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:47.89,Song,,0,0,5,,Ashimoto ga tora rete ite sora wa ureru bakaridatta
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.89,0:21:54.56,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:22:01.63,Song,,0,0,5,,Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.21,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2}So it will remain forever,\NAs I will remain forever so!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:08.22,Song,,0,0,5,,Konomama de īkai boku wa konomama de īkai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.21,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,75,,{\an2\fade(0,800)}So do we, the way we are now, \NWe surely will remain forever too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:15.68,Song,,0,0,5,,{\fade(0,800)}Kimi to konomama zutto konomama de īkai
